These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, coach, dancer, scientist
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, dunhill, siglo, davidoff
House: colonial, farmhouse, tower, art-deco
1. the art-deco house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
2. the dancer is on the left of the designer##1
3. the scientist is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
4. the designer is the prince-smoker##1
5. the prince-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
6. the colonial house is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
7. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Job    | coach  | scientist | dancer    | designer       |
| Cigar         | dunhill | davidoff    | siglo      | prince |
| House   | colonial   | tower | farmhouse | art-deco        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
House: modern, cottage, palace, wooden
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, alhambra, bolivar, dunhill
4 different games are played: backgammon, domino, snooker, scrabble
1. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
2. the wooden house is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
3. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the palace house##1
4. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
5. the person playing backgammon is the dannemann-smoker##1
6. the person playing scrabble is the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| House        | palace   | cottage | modern     | wooden      |
| Cigar         | alhambra | bolivar | dunhill | dannemann |
| Game   | domino    | scrabble   | snooker     | backgammon      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, hamster, lizard, guinea-pig
There 4 different types of food: avocado, lemon, cabbage, artichoke
House: farmhouse, ranch-style, craftsman, tower
1. the person eating lemon is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
2. the ranch-style house is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the person eating artichoke is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person eating cabbage##1
5. the tower house is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
6. the tower house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
7. the owner of the bird is the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Pet         | bird | hamster | lizard | guinea-pig |
| Food   | artichoke       | lemon    | avocado | cabbage     |
| House   | farmhouse | craftsman    | tower | ranch-style    |

