.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, family, scientific, sports
House: futuristic, victorian, colonial, palace
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, december, october, may
1. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the victorian house is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
5. the colonial house is on the far right##1
6. the futuristic house is the person watching scientific movies##1
7. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the colonial house##1
8. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre         | musical | sports | scientific | family |
| House       | victorian     | palace      | futuristic     | colonial      |
| Birthday   | december | june         | may      | october        |

