.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, architect, coach, doctor
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, boat, quad-bike, roller
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, salsa, hip-hop, d&b
1. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
2. the coach is on the far left##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
4. the fan of country is the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the teacher is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
6. the teacher is the person driving the boat##1
7. the doctor is the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Job         | coach   | doctor | architect  | teacher      |
| Transport   | quad-bike  | trike        | roller  | boat       |
| Music-Genre         | country | hip-hop    | salsa | d&b |

