.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, scrabble, billiard, bridge
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, tea, water, iced-tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, photography, puzzles, rock-climbing
1. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left##1
5. the person playing scrabble is on the far left##1
6. the person drinking water is the person playing billiard##1
7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
8. the person playing bridge is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Game           | scrabble | billiard | bridge | mah-jongg |
| Beverage   | iced-tea   | water  | tea | almond-milk   |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing   | reading     | puzzles | photography       |

