.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, train, tram, ship
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk, sprite, hot-chocolate
4 different games are played: bridge, chess, backgammon, monopoly
1. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the train is on the far right##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing chess##1
4. the person playing chess is the person driving the tram##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
8. the person drinking milk is the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Transport          | snowmobile  | ship | tram   | train     |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate | milk   | almond-milk  | sprite |
| Game   | backgammon         | bridge  | chess | monopoly  |

