.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, december, june, november
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, bellflower, marigold, dahlia
4 different pets are kept: frog, cat, rabbit, dog
1. the person who's birthday is in december is the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
6. the owner of the dog is the person who's birthday is in june##1
7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Birthday      | november | june     | august | december |
| Flower   | dahlia  | daffodil | marigold       | bellflower    |
| Pet   | cat   | dog | frog    | rabbit |

