.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
City: san-francisco, edinburgh, boston, new-york
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, lemonade, water, almond-milk
4 different pets are kept: snake, cat, rabbit, ferret
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking water##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| City          | boston        | new-york   | edinburgh  | san-francisco   |
| Beverage   | coffee         | almond-milk     | lemonade    | water       |
| Pet         | cat | snake | rabbit | ferret |

