.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, disco, funk, techno
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, skiing, volleyball, cycling
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, orange, coral, ebony
1. the fan of techno is the person who likes ebony##1
2. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
3. the fan of funk is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
4. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
6. the fan of funk is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | disco    | funk | techno | classical        |
| Sport       | cycling | cricket  | skiing | volleyball     |
| Color        | orange    | coral   | ebony  | turquise |

