4. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of trance##1
5. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person eating orange##1
6. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
7. the fan of hip-hop is the person eating carrot##1
8. the fan of jazz is the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| House         | futuristic  | gothic-revival | tower  | wooden |
| Music-Genre       | jazz | disco        | trance | hip-hop       |
| Food   | zucchini   | orange          | cherry          | carrot       |

