3. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
4. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
5. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
6. the person traveling to hannover is the person driving the car##1
7. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| City         | boston   | prague   | hannover | hamburg |
| Flower   | amaryllis | lily | iris   | sunflower |
| Transport   | bus     | subway  | car  | snowmobile  |

