.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-14::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, cranberry, pomegranate, grapes
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, april, october, march
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, begonia, rose, daffodil
1. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
6. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
7. the person eating pomegranate is on the far right##1
8. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Food   | cranberry   | grapes  | grapefruit    | pomegranate    |
| Birthday   | march | october  | december  | april |
| Flower     | daffodil  | begonia | rose | azalea        |

