3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person traveling to venice is the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person traveling to berlin##1
7. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| City          | hamburg     | nizza   | berlin | venice |
| Hobby   | video-games | reading | rock-climbing | camping   |
| Sport           | snowboarding    | cricket     | swimming      | soccer     |

