4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
7. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |    3    |      4      |
| Sport       | skateboarding | baseball | cycling | basketball |
| Pet         | cat | bird  | frog   | mouse      |
| Beverage   | 7up        | cola  | soy-milk   | sprite         |

