.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
4 different games are played: snooker, backgammon, go, mah-jongg
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, ivory, fuchsia, azure
House: victorian, gothic-revival, art-deco, ranch-style
1. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
2. the victorian house is on the left of the person playing go##1
3. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes orange is the art-deco house##1
6. the person who likes azure is on the far left##1
7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
8. the person who likes azure is on the left of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Game           | backgammon  | go  | snooker | mah-jongg |
| Color   | azure   | orange | ivory   | fuchsia      |
| House         | victorian | art-deco    | gothic-revival   | ranch-style         |

 